profile:
Award Winning Specialists!
416-236-8721

A&A Masonry is an award-winning Toronto based firm specializing in almost everything exterior.  Specialties include Stone work, Interlock, Interlocking, Paver stones, paving stones, Natural Stone, Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Masonry, brick repair, brick restoration, tuck pointing, waterproofing, foundation repairs, concrete steps, porches, walkways, caulking services (windows & doors), chimney repair and general exterior restorations for residential, commercial and industrial customers.

A&A is dedicated to providing the highest quality on every job. With a proud team of qualified artisans, we strive to complete every project in a timely and safe manner.

Our mission is to offer a unique and reliable service in anything Exterior within the Greater Toronto Area, differentiating ourselves from the competition by means of always delivering what we promise, on time and on budget.

Our commitment to excellence is our core value.
Customer satisfaction is our main goal, and we reach it every day by relying on our attention to customer service. By providing customized solutions for every job, we guarantee that we will never compromise on quality, safety and efficiency.

This approach together with our experience and knowledge allows us to effectively handle a wide variety of projects, from small to big, indoors or outdoors, renovations or repairs. 

We service:  Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Thornhill, Richmond Hill, York, North York, East York, Mimico, Hamilton, Brampton, Bolton and surrounding areas. 

For FREE ESTIMATE CALL: 416-236-8721

Being Masonry Contractors, Concrete Contractors, Stone  Contractors & Waterproofing Contractors we specialize in:
Stone work, Interlocking Natural Stone & Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Tuck Pointing, Chimney Repair, Chimney Rebuild, Chimney Restoration, tuckpointing, Brickwork, Brick Repair, Brick Replacement, Parging, Waterproofing, Foundation Repair, Concrete Resurfacing, Concrete Porches, Concrete Steps, Patios and Walkways, Flagstone, Cultured Stone, Caulking services (windows and doors), Masonry, Masonry repair, steps, concrete porches, concrete walkways and patios, caulking services.

profile:
Solocrete General Contracting Ltd. believes that quality, customer service and satisfaction are very important requirements to achieve the highest reputation and trust in this business.  We are constantly upgrading in order to give our customers the very best selection and quality in: stamp concrete, regular white concrete, coloured concrete, and aggregate/exposed concrete.  We also offer the specialized overlay of jewel stone.  Our products are ideal for driveways, walkways, curbs, gardening curbs, back patios, around pools, steps, pillars and overlays on porches.  Unique to Solocrete are the french curbs and the smooth and rough finishes of bull nosing on steps.   
Give your house a new look … Let Solocrete create it!

Josef Construction is a home renovation contractor located in Mississauga Area. We provide full services to customers looking to renovate their bathroom, basement, floor and kitchen, what ever you need. We also offer Landscaping and Custom Built Homes.

Josef Construction’s innovative home remodeling designs, meticulous craftsmanship, with a great deal of  professionalism as a general home contractor have made it possible for many residents in the Greater Toronto Area, and the suburbs.

These residents now enjoy a home that feels just right.

Our experienced construction team does amazing craftsmanship dedicated to providing the clients with complete satisfaction on each detailed job.  With all the qualified staff Josef Construction has successfully completed hundreds of commercial and residential projects

Founded by Nasim Soteri, Josef Construction became one of the home contracting companies that know how to deliver the job on time and on budget.

profile:
At Bestway Concrete Contractors we offer custom designed solutions for your residential projects. We are a fully-insured, locally-owned, family-run business that specializes in a range of concrete projects from stamped concrete to aggregate.

We ensure projects proceed with open communication and we pay strict attention to every detail, no matter how small, during every phase of every job.

We specialize in stamped concrete, regular white concrete, coloured concrete, and aggregate/exposed concrete.

Our workmanship covers everything from driveways, walkways, curbs, gardening curbs, back patios, around pools, steps, pillars and porches.

We customize our french curbs to each customers desire. Our bull noses are perfected with high quality stamps to get the best finish every time.
